    "body": "> Arg, the parser has issues with default values of non-optional parameters; as soon as they're not integers. Will need to check how to improve that.\r\n\r\nI get this is maybe not even a bug, if the parameter is required there can't be a default value. It needs to be written as optionnal to be able to set a default value.",
